<p><strong>坦克300</strong></p>
<p><strong>广州车展上市</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201107/e0724f9a71ab4f03af3aba0c43fe7be9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
